-  agent scanning: QUICK DISCOVERY ΓåÆ EXHAUSTIVE ΓåÆ CITATION REPAIR ΓåÆ KNOWN ITEM
-  ΓåÆ CITATION ΓåÆ AUTHOR ΓåÆ SNIPPET.
